==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pitter-patter
<hw>Pit"ter-pat`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sound like
that of alternating light beats. Also, a pattering of words.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pitter-patter</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Pitter-patter
<hw>Pit"ter-pat`ter</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>With, or with the sound
of, alternating light beats; <as>as, his heart went
<ex>pitter-patter</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pittle-pattle</ent>⟦br⟧
